猫（可自行买 TpLink GPON 的相关型号约 180 元左右），优先转让是 v 友自己的物业的朋友。\r\n```","content_rendered":"<pre><code class=\"language-bash\">早些年托朋友的关系，在广州联通搞了一条家用宽带（下行 100Mbps，上行 10Mbps ），带有动态公网 ip，因为卖房搬家的原因现在住房的地方没有联通的宽带资源，只能用电信的宽带，现在以较低的价格出让这条宽带。\n注意：\n1.宽带跟有捆绑我的一个手机号好，不能过户。\n2.因为有动态公网 ip，不要用来建站什么的违规用途，我之前是用来 NAS 远程访问及备份的。\n3.短期内我现在住的小区不会有联通的宽带资源，所以我希望约定转让宽带的使用权的期间是 2 年以上，可以每 2 年续续费一次，或者一次性签订 2 年以上的若干年的使用期限。\n4.费用是 480 元 /年，移机的费用 100 元交联通营业厅，不带光猫（可自行买 TpLink GPON 的相关型号约 180 元左右），优先转让是 v 友自己的物业的朋友。\n</code></pre>\n","last_modified":1633233528,"replies":6,"id":805735},{"node":{"avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/70ef/df2e/17_large.png?m=1629391403","name":"create","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/70ef/df2e/17_normal.png?m=1629391403","title":"分享创造","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/create","topics":16762,"footer":"","header":"欢迎你在这里发布自己的最新作品！","title_alternative":"Create","avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/70ef/df2e/17_mini.png?m=1629391403","stars":4060,"aliases":[],"root":false,"id":17,"parent_node_name":"geek"},"member":{"username":"stevenlei","website":null,"github":null,"psn":null,"avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/5626/ca76/186434_mini.png?m=1582170222","bio":null,"url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/stevenlei","tagline":null,"twitter":null,"created":1470850005,"avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/5626/ca76/186434_mini.png?m=1582170222","avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/5626/ca76/186434_mini.png?m=1582170222","location":null,"btc":null,"id":186434},"last_reply_by":"0312birdzhang","last_touched":1633246772,"title":"用 CSS 画出 iPhone 13 Pro","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/805719","created":1633224945,"content":"昨天放假无聊，试着把 iPhone 13 Pro 用 CSS 画出来，效果如下：\r\n\r\n![]( http://codingstartup.com/assets/iphone-13-pro-css-drawing.png)\r\n\r\n源代码：[https://codepen.io/stevenlei/pen/jOwRxpY]( https://codepen.io/stevenlei/pen/jOwRxpY)\r\n\r\n视频：[BiliBili]( https://www.bilibili.com/video/BV12u411f7TM/) [YouTube]( https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=JK_58oa3HM0)\